<h6 id="the-hiaccounting-team"><em>The HiAccounting Team</em></h6>

<p> </p>

<p><strong>About HiAccounting</strong></p>

<p>HiAccounting’s comprehensive finance, accounting and tax services provide small to mid-size Hawaii companies with professional corporate accounting without the cost and management challenges associated with an in-house bookkeeping and accounting department. HiAccounting has been named one of the fastest 50 businesses in the state in 2015 &amp; 2016, and received a BBB Torch Award. It is a member of The Hawaii Group family of companies.</p>

<p>Learn more at <a href="http://hi-accounting.com">www.hi-accounting.com</a>.</p>
